Purpose:   View for creating (inserting) or updating Product objects
Contains:  Model, ViewData for page title, Layout specification, Html, asp tag helpers, JavaScript
Author:    Martin Dwyer
Created:   2022-08-17
Last Edit: 2022-08-22
By:        Martin Dwyer
